column2: Donate your money to the investor!
I'll be on your turret in a few seconds.
We need a scout to find the alephs.
Lay low and go for constructors.
Our base is under attack.   Request assistance.
Capturing base, get ready to launch!
Don't forget to take along your rescue probes!
Stay out of the middle aleph!
Sorry ya'll, my ISP dropped me.
What are you saving up for?
It'll be a couple more minutes.
Just a sec...waiting for a couple more people.
So, nice weather..how's the youngens? Let's play this thing!
It's late ... gotta go. Night ya'll.
Great game. How about a rematch?
Even up, or I'll even it up.
I'd love to, but I'm podded.
I said no, and I mean it!
Let's just bug out and call it even, ok?
Look, I don't have time for this.
Hey maybe you haven't been keeping up on current events...
What the hell are we supposed to use man, harsh language?
You want a piece of me?
Ripcord... last resort for the desperate.
You'll be sorry you did that
Easer than shooting fish in a barrel!
You're good but not that good.
Did IQs just drop sharply while I was away?
Now you see me, now you don't.
Ow, that's gonna leave a mark!
Stop your grinnin' and drop your linen.
We will not tolerate this behavior.
I'm the King of the Hill!
That's it man...Game over man, game over!
Let's go people, they ain't paying us by the hour...
They ain't paying us enough for this man...
The aleph is mined and droned!
How far is their base from the aleph?
It'll be a couple more minutes.
Oh they see me..I've been spotted.
Meet me at the jump point.
Nanites, launch and wait for bomber.
Defend our miners,  they are getting hammered!
We have a traitor in our midst.
I'm out of ammo.. hmm, interesting.
